## External Services Used (At Runtime)

The following services are queried by certain apps over HTTPS. No data is sent except the minimum needed to fulfill the user's request. No telemetry, tracking, or analytics are transmitted.

| App | Service | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `tides.html` | NOAA CO-OPS API (api.tidesandcurrents.noaa.gov) | Tide predictions for US coastal stations |
| `barcode.html` | Open Food Facts (world.openfoodfacts.org) | Product lookup by EAN/UPC |
| `offline_maps.html` | OpenStreetMap, OpenTopoMap, ESRI, CARTO | Map tile rendering (cached locally for offline use) |
| `weather.html` | National Weather Service API (api.weather.gov) | Weather forecasts (US only) |
| `news_*.html` | Various RSS feeds | News headlines |
| `nfl/nba/nhl/mls.html` | ESPN API, sportsdata.io, statsapi.mlb.com | Sports scores and stats |
| `gemini_terminal.html` | Google Gemini API (generativelanguage.googleapis.com) | LLM-assisted research (user-supplied API key) |

All other apps function fully offline.

